title: James Gunn is Making Suicide Squad 2! - The Kinda Funny Morning Show 10.09.18
description:
Test out Gabi for free at http://gabi.com/MORNING

Robinhood is giving listeners free stock to help build your portfolio. Sign up at http://morningshow.robinhood.com

Get your first refill pack free at http://getquip.com/KFMS

Nick, Joey, and Greg talk about the reveal of Batwoman’s New costume and weigh-in on James Gunn’s move to the DC cinematic universe with Suicide Squad 2.

Time Stamps - 
-First look at CW's Batwoman (26:10 mins)
-Daredevil season 3 trailer (36:03 mins)
-James Gunn is moving to DC and will write the next suicide squad film (50:50 mins)
-La Croix news teaser (54:25 mins)

Thanks to https://www.twitter.com/kumailh for our timestamps!

Subscribe! http://www.youtube.com/kindafunny?sub_confirmation=1

Support us and get the shows early here! http://www.patreon.com/kindafunny

Check out our store! http://www.kindafunny.com/store

Follow us on Twitter!
Greg - http://www.twitter.com/GameOverGreggy
Tim - http://www.twitter.com/TimGettys
Nick - http://www.twitter.com/Nick_Scarpino
Kinda Funny - http://www.twitter.com/KindaFunnyVids

Every day Greg Miller, Tim Gettys, and Nick Scarpino talk about the biggest stories in nerd culture.

Music by Tonedeff - http://www.QN5.com
